msgctxt "QL_Gerudo_Ch_Poison_Desc"
msgid ""
"Dalia has been working hard to start an orchard,\n"
"but garbage keeps appearing in her water\n"
"source, so her efforts are all for naught.\n"
"What sort of <1.se_co>vile polluter<2.re_co> would toss his or her\n"
"garbage away with such indifference?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "QL_Gerudo_Ch_Poison_Finish"
msgid ""
"Dalia planted the wildberries she received from\n"
"Calyban and said that it's OK to pick them\n"
"once they grow in.\n"
"\n"
"With the source of the water pollution cleared\n"
"up, all that's left to do is wait for the wildberries\n"
"to grow."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "QL_Gerudo_Ch_Poison_Name"
msgid "The Mystery Polluter"
msgstr ""

#. 1: set_colour (red)
#. 2: reset_colour
msgctxt "QL_Gerudo_Ch_Poison_Step1"
msgid ""
"The water source got polluted with garbage, so\n"
"the water has become unusable. The cause\n"
"turned out to be a woman throwing melon rinds\n"
"away in the waterway upstream. She says if you\n"
"bring her <1.se_co>10 wildberries <2.re_co>from the snow-topped\n"
"peaks of the Gerudo Highlands, she'll stop\n"
"eating so many melons..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "QL_Gerudo_Ch_Poison_Step2"
msgid ""
"The water source was polluted with garbage, so\n"
"the water became unusable. The cause turned\n"
"out to be a woman throwing melon rinds away\n"
"in the waterway upstream. In exchange for 10\n"
"wildberries, she agreed to stop eating melons.\n"
"Maybe the water will clear up now.\n"
"\n"
"Hurry back and report to Dalia."
msgstr ""

